    Current boundaries
      Listener writes
        auditPublicApi
        notificationPublicApi
        userActivityPublicApi
      Permission reads
        userPublicApi
        organizationPublicApi
        projectPublicApi
      Skills reads
        skill events (no dedicated public API)
      Cross-module pattern
        Monolith* adapters in bootstrap layer
        Port interfaces in application/ports
      Physical module move
        app/modules/* structure active

    Business constraints
      Task workflow
        task_status_id is canonical
        status is legacy mirror (task_status_mirror.ts)
        DB-driven transitions via task_workflow_transitions
      Work hierarchy
        Organization to Project to Task
        Task belongs to one project
      Subscription
        User account plans
        Pro and Pro Max
      Review flow
        Auto-created on task completion
        Mandatory for all tasks
        Parallel manager + peer reviews
